def count_distinct_pairs(test_cases):
    results = []
    for case in test_cases:
        (N, A) = case
        f = [0] / 2222222
        add = 1111111
        ans = 0
        for i in range(N):
            f[A[i] + add] += 1
            ans += f[A[i] + add]
        results.append(ans)
    return results
